{"tid":1144074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"KOL 拍片承認落藥性侵Model","createTime":"2019-05-08T01:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T07:04:21.000Z","uid":102732,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c9fa418d7c5b5ae02c942f2f0b633d678a1971","tid":1144074,"uid":102732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:39:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3kol-%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%90%BD%E8%97%A5%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5model-060544946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3kol-%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5model-060544946.html&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=ded52679\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3kol-%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%90%BD%E8%97%A5%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5model-060544946.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣youtuber市場大，有一批被稱為「知識型網紅」，<br />\n憑住本身嘅學問，令觀眾有片睇又有嘢學，<br />\n加上專業形象吸引到廣告客戶，唔少都快速竄紅。<br />\n「理科太太」就係好例子。<br />\n<br />\n另一位以揭示社會另一面嘅「知識型網紅」「教授鼠鼠」，<br />\n曾經拍片講及虛擬幣、夾公仔機騙局、大麻等邊緣話題，提醒年青人要小心，<br />\n佢嘅Youtube channel有成10萬人訂閱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nprNjHfGeB.ONl7.Mzqw0Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDIy/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/ade38806a47d0bcadfd7a3b8a5dfc3c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnprNjHfGeB.ONl7.Mzqw0Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDIy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2Fade38806a47d0bcadfd7a3b8a5dfc3c7&h=5466a882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，「教授鼠鼠」早幾日就上載咗條片，<br />\n以「一個真摯誠懇的懺悔，我做了錯誤的事情，希望大家引以為戒」為題，<br />\n承認自己落藥迷暈女模特兒後，再乘機性侵。<br />\n片段入面，「教授鼠鼠」指自己欺騙姓王女模特兒服用「放鬆藥物」，<br />\n令對方昏迷，並趁機發生性行為。<br />\n事後王因為「逃避羞憤感覺」，嘗試與「教授鼠鼠」交往。<br />\n唔止咁，「教授鼠鼠」借用王女嘅車約其他女子幽會，<br />\n又住喺王女嘅地方，但就出po同人講對方係自己包養。<br />\n最後「教授鼠鼠」發誓唔會再使用毒品對女生落藥，強調呢條片內容唔係有人迫佢先講。<br />\n佢亦願意接受同負起法律責任，並向王女道歉。<br />\n但係條片上載冇耐，「教授鼠鼠」就刪片，<br />\n並私訊王女因為阿媽睇到而將片段下架。<br />\n而王女亦有出po將二人對話內容公開，<br />\n又指至少有5位情況類似嘅受害人聯絡過佢，仲估計受害人可能過百！<br />\n睇嚟有關方面會介入呢單案，後續新聞應該唔少。<br />\n去台灣會落夜店嘅朋友，自己睇路啦。<br />\n<br />\n又係台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f9bc245bdca27aab9fb078357200ff5393b63f","tid":1144074,"uid":42487,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"台灣日扑夜扑遲早超越13億人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d8e219f65a1950d8d2ed9735d322089618b5ff","tid":1144074,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"goal！"},{"pid":"60bcd25de8f371fcd4dc3efd3f6daebd3cfa0a84","tid":1144074,"uid":9726,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9383fe999c73e56a2ac0d4f1d4fe46f9e987c34b","tid":1144074,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cad79627b44b2cab34a6ecf6d354fc20868fb4","tid":1144074,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89122f63e0c730b4e65dbb21b978df76fe50eea","tid":1144074,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:35:42.000Z","msg":"咁鍾意拍片竟然無片？"},{"pid":"a025c1e5ffac2ff313cdd43f2c6aadf26e1d500e","tid":1144074,"uid":107913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T02:36:49.000Z","msg":"起碼都貼張相出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447aceb4e9767e3b670c9d908cd5b9306bfb8e9f","tid":1144074,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,